Diphthongs
Apart from the "hard-coded" diphthongs above, there are quite a few vowel pairs that can appear together although they're not "proper" diphthongs. Just be aware that in some cases a 'j' must be inserted between them. The 'j' sometimes appears in print but not always 
	flýja = f l i: j a 
	kría = k r i: j a
This also occurs with certain dipthongs
	ææ = ai j ai
